<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Whispr — Share Your Thoughts</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Whispr is a platform to share your feelings, thoughts, emotions and ideas with the world. Express yourself freely.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        :root {
            --bg: #0a0a0f;
            --surface: #13131a;
            --border: #1e1e2e;
            --accent: #7c6aff;
            --accent2: #ff6ab0;
            --text: #e8e8f0;
            --muted: #6b6b80;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated gradient background */
        .bg-glow {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .bg-glow::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -20%;
            left: -10%;
            width: 60%;
            height: 60%;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: drift1 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        .bg-glow::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 55%;
            height: 55%;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(255, 106, 176, 0.14) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: drift2 14s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes drift1 {
            from {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
            }

            to {
                transform: translate(5%, 8%);
            }
        }

        @keyframes drift2 {
            from {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
            }

            to {
                transform: translate(-5%, -8%);
            }
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            padding: 0.5rem 1.4rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            padding: 0.5rem 1.4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #9b6aff);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 7rem 2rem 5rem;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #a89aff;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
        }

        .hero-badge span {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {

            0%,
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }

            50% {
                opacity: 0.3;
            }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.08;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.1s both;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent2) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 400;
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.2s both;
        }

        .hero-cta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.3s both;
        }

        .btn-hero {
            padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #9b6aff);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.25s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-hero:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .btn-hero-ghost {
            padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

        .btn-hero-ghost:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Preview cards */
        .preview-section {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            padding: 2rem 2rem 6rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
        }

        .preview-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
            width: 260px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .preview-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .preview-card:nth-child(2) {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
        }

        .preview-card:nth-child(2):hover {
            transform: translateY(-18px);
        }

        .card-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .av1 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c6aff, #9b6aff);
        }

        .av2 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6ab0, #ff8c6a);
        }

        .av3 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6affe0, #6ab0ff);
            color: #000;
        }

        .card-username {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #a89aff;
        }

        .card-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card-likes {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .card-likes span {
            color: #ff6ab0;
        }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            padding: 4rem 4rem 6rem;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .features h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .features-sub {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* CTA Banner */
        .cta-banner {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            margin: 0 4rem 6rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.15), rgba(255, 106, 176, 0.1));
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 106, 255, 0.25);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-banner h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .cta-banner p {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        footer span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav {
                padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .features {
                padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .cta-banner {
                margin: 0 1rem 3rem;
                padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .preview-card:nth-child(3) {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="bg-glow"></div>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">Whispr</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a class="btn-outline" href="/login">Log In</a>
            <a class="btn-primary" href="/signup">Sign Up Free</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-badge">
            <span></span>
            A safe space for your thoughts
        </div>
        <h1>
            Your thoughts<br>
            deserve to be <span class="gradient-text">heard.</span>
        </h1>
        <p>
            Whispr is a platform where you can freely share your feelings, emotions, ideas and stories — with people who
            actually listen.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="btn-hero" href="/signup">Start Sharing →</a>
            <a class="btn-hero-ghost" href="/login">I have an account</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Preview Cards -->
    <div class="preview-section">
        <div class="preview-card">
            <div class="card-author">
                <div class="avatar av1">AK</div>
                <span class="card-username">@aarav_k</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text">"Sometimes the bravest thing you can do is just keep going, even when everything feels
                heavy."</p>
            <div class="card-likes">❤️ <span>142</span> likes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="preview-card">
            <div class="card-author">
                <div class="avatar av2">SR</div>
                <span class="card-username">@sara_r</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text">"I finally told someone how I really felt today. It was terrifying. It was also the
                most freeing thing I've ever done."</p>
            <div class="card-likes">❤️ <span>289</span> likes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="preview-card">
            <div class="card-author">
                <div class="avatar av3">MJ</div>
                <span class="card-username">@mjay</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text">"3am thoughts hit different. The world is quiet and your mind is the loudest thing in
                the room."</p>
            <div class="card-likes">❤️ <span>97</span> likes</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="features">
        <h2>Why Whispr?</h2>
        <p class="features-sub">A place built for real human expression.</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
                <h3>Express Freely</h3>
                <p>Share what's on your mind without judgment. Your words matter here.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">❤️</div>
                <h3>Feel Connected</h3>
                <p>Like and engage with posts from people who feel exactly what you feel.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">✏️</div>
                <h3>Own Your Story</h3>
                <p>Edit or remove your posts anytime. You're always in control of your voice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
                <h3>Safe & Private</h3>
                <p>Your account is yours. Only you can edit or delete what you post.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Banner -->
    <div class="cta-banner">
        <h2>Ready to share your story?</h2>
        <p>Join thousands of people expressing themselves every day.</p>
        <a class="btn-hero" href="/signup">Create Your Account →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        Made with <span>♥</span> · Whispr © 2025
    </footer>

</body>

</html>